     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet IDC10DPDCancer</b></p><a name=\"IDC10DPDCancer\"> </a><a name=\"hcIDC10DPDCancer\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/SKSCodeCollection</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html#SKSCodeCollection-lips_mouth_throat\">lips_mouth_throat</a></td><td>Mundhule og svælg (DC00-DC14)</td><td>Kræft i læber, mundhule og svælg (DC00-DC14)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html#SKSCodeCollection-colon_rectum\">colon_rectum</a></td><td>Tyktarm og endetarm (DC18-DC20)</td><td>Kræft i tyktarm og endetarm (DC18-DC20)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html#SKSCodeCollection-trachea_bronchi_lung\">trachea_bronchi_lung</a></td><td>Lunge, bronkier og luftrør (DC33-DC34)</td><td>Kræft i luftrøret og bronkier og lunge (DC33-DC34)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html#SKSCodeCollection-uterus\">uterus</a></td><td>Livmoder (inkl. uspecifik) (DC54-DC55)</td><td>Kræft i livmoderen (inkl. uspecifik) (DC54-DC55)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html#SKSCodeCollection-ovary_fallopian_tube\">ovary_fallopian_tube</a></td><td>Æggestokke (DC56+DC570-DC574)</td><td>Kræft i æggestok og æggeleder (DC56+DC570-DC574)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html#SKSCodeCollection-kidney_pelvis_ureter\">kidney_pelvis_ureter</a></td><td>Nyre, nyrebækken og urinleder (DC64-DC66)</td><td>Kræft i nyre, nyrebækken og urinleder (DC64-DC66)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html#SKSCodeCollection-central_nervous_system\">central_nervous_system</a></td><td>Hjerne og centralnervesystem (DC70-DC72+DC751-DC753)</td><td>Kræft i centralnervesystem (DC70-DC72+DC751-DC753)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html#SKSCodeCollection-non_hodgkin\">non_hodgkin</a></td><td>Non-hodgkin malignt lymform (DC82-DC85)</td><td>Non-hodking malignt lymform (DC82-DC85)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html#SKSCodeCollection-leukemia\">leukemia</a></td><td>Leukæmi (DC91-DC95)</td><td>Leukæmi (DC91-DC95)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html#SKSCodeCollection-mesotel_tissue\">mesotel_tissue</a></td><td>Sarkomer og andre bløddele (DC45-DC49)</td><td>Kræft i mesotel, bindevæv og andet bløddelsvæv (DC45-DC49)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html#SKSCodeCollection-unspecific\">unspecific</a></td><td>Ukendt kræft</td><td>Kræft med dårligt specificerede, sekundære, ikke specificerede og ukendte lokalisationer (DC76-DC80+DD37-DD48)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKSCodeCollection.html#SKSCodeCollection-other_cancer_diseases\">other_cancer_diseases</a></td><td>Anden kræft (C76-80+D37-D48)</td><td>Ikke-kræft sygdomme</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/SKS</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-DC15\">DC15</a></td><td>Spiserør (DC15)</td><td>Kræft i spiserøret</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-DC16\">DC16</a></td><td>Mavesæk (DC16)</td><td>Kræft i mavesækken</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-DC17\">D